---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Refund Policy — Resonance.OS">

  <section class="s-hero">
    <span class="lbl">// LEGAL</span>
    <h1 class="hero-h1">Refund<br>Policy</h1>
    <p class="hero-meta">
      SAJA Creative (trading as Resonance.OS) · KvK 98592106<br>
      De Stringen 16, 9162 EX Ballum, The Netherlands<br>
      Last updated: 28 May 2026
    </p>
  </section>

  <div class="slash-sep" aria-hidden="true">// </div>

  <section class="s-doc" style="background: var(--bg-alt);">

    <aside class="doc-sidebar">
      <p class="doc-sidebar-label">// Contents</p>
      <nav class="doc-toc">
        <a href="#s1">1. Resonance.ID</a>
        <a href="#s2">2. Resonance.SITE</a>
        <a href="#s3">3. How to request a refund</a>
        <a href="#s4">4. Problems with your deliverable</a>
        <a href="#s5">5. Your statutory rights</a>
        <a href="#s6">6. Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </aside>

    <div class="doc-content">

      <div class="doc-section" id="s1">
        <p class="doc-section-n">01</p>
        <h2 class="doc-section-h">Resonance.ID</h2>
        <p class="doc-p">Resonance.ID is a personalised digital product, cultivated by hand specifically for you based on your intake. Because of this, our refund approach is tied to whether cultivation has started.</p>

        <h3 class="doc-section-sh">Before cultivation begins — full refund available.</h3>
        <p class="doc-p">After you pay, you are asked to complete your intake (audio or written). In the window <strong>between your payment and the moment we begin cultivating your Resonance.ID</strong>, you may change your mind and request a full refund. Simply email us at <a href="mailto:info@resonance-os.studio" style="color:var(--accent)">info@resonance-os.studio</a>.</p>

        <h3 class="doc-section-sh">After cultivation begins — no refund.</h3>
        <p class="doc-p">Once we have started cultivating your Resonance.ID, the work is personalised and underway, and the purchase is non-refundable. Cultivation begins once we start working on your deliverable following receipt of your completed intake.</p>

        <h3 class="doc-section-sh">If you never complete your intake.</h3>
        <p class="doc-p">If you pay but do not submit your intake, cultivation cannot begin. You may request a full refund at any time before cultivation starts. We may, after a reasonable period, reach out to remind you — but we will not begin cultivation, and therefore will not withhold a refund, until you have submitted your intake.</p>

        <h3 class="doc-section-sh">Your EU right of withdrawal and how it applies.</h3>
        <p class="doc-p">As a consumer in the EU, you normally have a 14-day right to withdraw from a purchase. For digital products and services that begin immediately at your request, this right can lawfully be waived so that delivery can start without waiting 14 days.</p>
        <p class="doc-p">At checkout, you will be asked to confirm two things:</p>
        <ul class="doc-list">
          <li class="doc-list-item">
            <span class="doc-list-item-dot">●</span>
            <span>that you want cultivation of your Resonance.ID to begin as soon as you submit your intake, and</span>
          </li>
          <li class="doc-list-item">
            <span class="doc-list-item-dot">●</span>
            <span>that you understand and agree that, by doing so, you lose your 14-day right of withdrawal once cultivation has begun.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="doc-p">Until cultivation begins, your right to a full refund (as described above) remains. This policy does not take away any statutory right you have that cannot lawfully be waived.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="doc-section" id="s2">
        <p class="doc-section-n">02</p>
        <h2 class="doc-section-h">Resonance.SITE</h2>
        <p class="doc-p">Resonance.SITE is a custom service engagement governed by a separate written agreement. Its refund terms are:</p>
        <ul class="doc-list">
          <li class="doc-list-item">
            <span class="doc-list-item-dot">●</span>
            <span><strong>Deposit:</strong> The deposit payable before work begins is <strong>non-refundable</strong>. It reserves your project slot and covers the initial strategy and setup work.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="doc-list-item">
            <span class="doc-list-item-dot">●</span>
            <span><strong>Balance:</strong> The remaining balance is <strong>refundable up to design sign-off</strong> — meaning the point at which you approve the agreed design direction. After design sign-off, the balance is non-refundable, as the build work then proceeds on the basis of your approval.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="doc-list-item">
            <span class="doc-list-item-dot">●</span>
            <span>The specific deposit amount, milestones, and sign-off point are defined in your separate written agreement.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="doc-section" id="s3">
        <p class="doc-section-n">03</p>
        <h2 class="doc-section-h">How to request a refund</h2>
        <p class="doc-p">Email <a href="mailto:info@resonance-os.studio" style="color:var(--accent)">info@resonance-os.studio</a> with:</p>
        <ul class="doc-list">
          <li class="doc-list-item">
            <span class="doc-list-item-dot">●</span>
            <span>the name and email used for the purchase, and</span>
          </li>
          <li class="doc-list-item">
            <span class="doc-list-item-dot">●</span>
            <span>the product purchased.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="doc-p">We will confirm whether a refund applies under this policy and, where it does, process it to your original payment method. Refunds are typically processed within 14 days of approval; the time for the funds to appear depends on your bank or card provider.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="doc-section" id="s4">
        <p class="doc-section-n">04</p>
        <h2 class="doc-section-h">Problems with your deliverable</h2>
        <p class="doc-p">This policy covers changes of mind and cancellations. If you believe there is a genuine error or defect in what we delivered — something that is wrong, not merely something you would have preferred differently — contact us at <a href="mailto:info@resonance-os.studio" style="color:var(--accent)">info@resonance-os.studio</a> and we will work with you in good faith to put it right. This is separate from the refund rules above and does not affect your statutory rights.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="doc-section" id="s5">
        <p class="doc-section-n">05</p>
        <h2 class="doc-section-h">Your statutory rights</h2>
        <p class="doc-p">Nothing in this policy limits or removes your mandatory rights as a consumer under Dutch and EU law. Where this policy and your statutory rights differ, your statutory rights prevail.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="doc-section" id="s6">
        <p class="doc-section-n">06</p>
        <h2 class="doc-section-h">Contact</h2>
        <div class="doc-contact">
          <p>
            SAJA Creative (Resonance.OS)<br>
            De Stringen 16, 9162 EX Ballum, The Netherlands<br>
            KvK 98592106<br>
            <a href="mailto:info@resonance-os.studio">info@resonance-os.studio</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</Base>
